sellerCard.description:
Hi, I'm Inam founder of InaTechSolution. I've more than 7 years of experience in website design and development. InaTechSolution has a team of highly skilled professionals. We specialize in website design, website development, ecommerce, NFT website, and landing page.

We're building high-quality, user-friendly, and completely responsive wordpress websites according to the buyer's custom requirements.

Our mission is to provide 100% satisfaction to our clients. We'll guide you throughout the project and after that as well. Let's get in touch and start working on your dream website.

Thank you

questionsAndAnswers.question: How can I see your portfolio?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I have design and developed many website with complete satisfaction of my clients. Please contact me I'll be send you my detailed portfolio.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Before get to start.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: To start on your website. I'll ask you some question about your business and competitor. So that I get your point and I'll put these points in web design that meet your aspection.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I get hosting and domain for free in this package?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I'll not provide hosting and domain free in this. But I give you better suggestion which hosting provider is better for your website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Should I provide you hosting and domain details for you to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, It's not mandatory to get start. I'll upload the website on my hosting. There you can see my progress and when your satisfied. Then I'll migrate your website from my hosting to your hosting and domain.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I edit my website without any technical knowledge?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can edit your website easily without any technical knowledge. You can add, delete and update content on your website. I'll provide you complete guide lines.

questionsAndAnswers.question: If there is an issue after the project completion. will you resolve it?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I'll try to fix ASAP. In addition, I'll provide you 30 days free support.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you give me discounted price?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can give you discounts according to your website and budget. We discuss about it and I'll give you less price that meet your budget.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will the website be SEO friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, the website and url of the website will be SEO friendly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: If you have more question?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Click on the Contact button and send your query. I'll reply you ASAP. I'll be happy to assist you. Thank you
